com.ptc.windchill.option.choicecomponent

Class ChoiceSuggestionBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ptc.windchill.option.choicecomponent.ChoiceSuggestionBean

  • public class ChoiceSuggestionBean
extends java.lang.Object
    An info bean class which contains Choice, Option and Alias information. The Choice, Option and Alias information is based on the query result returned according to the input search String from UIs supporting Auto-suggest.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
